SCOPE
- Stack: Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, React Server Components, Tailwind, shadcn/ui optional.
- State: server components first; client components only when cần interactivity.
- Forms: react-hook-form + zod schema (shared @/lib/validators).

CODING
- Foldering: app/(routes)/page.tsx, app/api/*, components/ui/*, lib/*, hooks/*, styles/*.
- Styling: Tailwind utility-first; avoid inline styles if có class.
- Accessibility: label/aria, keyboard nav; test with Tab.
- Data fetching: cache by default; revalidate tags or ISR; streaming cho trang lớn.
- i18n: next-intl or built-in; keep copy tại messages/*.json.
- Error: use error.tsx + not-found.tsx per route; show user-friendly boundaries.

PERF
- Image via next/image, proper sizes; dynamic import for heavy components.
- Avoid blocking requests in client; prefer server actions or route handlers.

TEST
- Vitest/RTL cho components; Playwright basic happy-path flows.

DELIVERABLE
- When building a feature: produce route tree, component list, sample UI (skeleton), and tests.
